    "A private window into your recovery, sleep and strain — read straight from your strap, kept only on this Mac.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "A private window into your recovery, sleep and strain — read straight from your strap, kept only on this Mac."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein privater Blick auf deine Erholung, deinen Schlaf und deine Belastung — direkt vom Strap gelesen und nur auf diesem Mac gespeichert."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A standalone companion for your WHOOP. Everything stays on this device — your history, your live stream, your numbers. Nothing is uploaded. NOOP is an independent, experimental project, not the WHOOP app.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "A standalone companion for your WHOOP. Everything stays on this device — your history, your live stream, your numbers. Nothing is uploaded. NOOP is an independent, experimental project, not the WHOOP app."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein eigenständiger Begleiter für dein WHOOP. Alles bleibt auf diesem Gerät — deine Historie, dein Live-Stream, deine Werte. Nichts wird hochgeladen. NOOP ist ein unabhängiges, experimentelles Projekt, nicht die WHOOP-App."
          }
        }
      }
    },
